### Logic Layer
#### [MODIFY] [utils.js](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/스위치웹서비스/daily-habit-tracker/src/utils.js)
- Update [getTodayDate()](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EC%8A%A4%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%9B%B9%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4/daily-habit-tracker/src/utils.js#55-59) to return `YYYY-MM-DD` in **Local Time**.

